{"tid":745291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV 收視創新高　世盃決賽最高 26.6點　TVB收視最低 2點","createTime":"2018-07-16T15:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T15:47:46.000Z","uid":17506,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8207b23e8bf4d62f8a95b634bdcf36e01857f1d3","tid":745291,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T15:25:02.000Z","msg":"世界盃冠軍戰法國對克羅地亞，ViuTV昨晚11時直播法國對克羅地亞的決賽，收視創下ViuTV開台以來最高紀錄。ViuTV公布，昨晚決賽時段，ViuTV錄得平均收視24.4點，最高更加有26.6點（約177萬人次），創下ViuTV開台以來的平均和最高收視紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n另外，網絡平台串流收播率高達41萬次。<br />\n<br />\n據蘋果日報報道，無綫昨晚9點至11點半播出電影《使徒行者》應戰，平均 15點（98萬人次）；11點半《晚間新聞》平均4點（26萬人次）；11時50分至凌晨2點的兩集《刑事偵緝檔案IV》只得2點（13萬人次）。<br />\n<br />\nViuTV 收視創新高　世盃決賽最高 26.6點　TVB收視最低 2點 <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/media/%E4%B8%96%E7%9B%83%E5%8A%A9-viutv-%E6%94%B6%E8%A6%96%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E6%B1%BA%E8%B3%BD%E6%94%B6%E8%A6%96%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%9826-6%E9%BB%9E-tvb-%E6%94%B6%E8%A6%96%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E2%E9%BB%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%259B%2583%25E5%258A%25A9-viutv-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%259826-6%25E9%25BB%259E-tvb-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%258E2%25E9%25BB%259E%2F&d=592NbAX12gRHz7hn00hMX4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=67f5fcf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2F%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%259B%2583%25E5%258A%25A9-viutv-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598-%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%259826-6%25E9%25BB%259E-tvb-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25A6%2596%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%258E2%25E9%25BB%259E%2F&h=2da84144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/media/%E4%B8%96%E7%9B%83%E5%8A%A9-viutv-%E6%94%B6%E8%A6%96%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E6%B1%